{"tid":629983,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"練習派重口味感情膠,有請大家賜酒","createTime":"2018-04-15T07:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T08:25:08.000Z","uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d78850585287f7888d2052b41a2df7eb84420c3","tid":629983,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:31:49.000Z","msg":"首先大家不論男女,有無想過可以與喜歡的人 或 與討厭的人做愛?<br />\n今日無聊一想<br />\n1。如果有日我性轉換是美女如何被20幾個強壯大屌的蝻輪姦。<br />\n2。被20幾個蝻用 人肉三文治 連同自己女朋友一起強姦。<br />\n3。女朋友當臉被一個高大英俊的白人搶走,女朋友更親手send情慾短片示威和分手第二天收到女朋友的結婚移民短訊。<br />\n4。同上,但角色相反。<br />\n5。與英俊的男同事搞基(情慾或強姦)。<br />\n6。強姦 或 追求女同事。<br />\n7。用老師身份在女校開後宮。<br />\n8。同其他人輪姦街上見到的美女。<br />\n<br />\n這個幻想止不住,有無其他提材?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe9d8b78e46b62d324f0800877de5a2a52c5e9b","tid":629983,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"樓豬屎眼被人開發埋"},{"pid":"876168b4fb6d8afd6a4f49ef433e01d7712995f1","tid":629983,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfe9d8b78e46b62d324f0800877de5a2a52c5e9b","tid":629983,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"樓豬屎眼被人開發埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/153919_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F153919_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=43a382bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62cf85bade1ccd685951548b156267e36c865989","tid":629983,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfe9d8b78e46b62d324f0800877de5a2a52c5e9b","tid":629983,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"樓豬屎眼被人開發埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:25:08.000Z","msg":"那人是我自己"}]}